## Final reminder

The goal is a diagram that a senior engineer would point at during an
incident review and say “yes, this is what actually happens.” Not a diagram
that looks impressive. Not a diagram that shows everything. A diagram that
is correct, focused, and traceable to source.

Phase 1 first. Always Phase 1 first.